Test suite used is Catch2 : https://github.com/catchorg/Catch2

Tests are compiled and executable tests places in build/tests/

The following arguments may be useful when running the test executable
 - <test exe> "Test name"  # runs all tests that match given name
 - <test exe> "*est nam*"  # runs all tests that contain the substring
 - <test exe> [tag]        # runs all tests that have the given tag
